<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>UK Visa Support | The Admission Architect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons|Material+Icons+Outlined" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style> body { padding-top: 0 !important; } </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="landing-hero" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.9), rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-8d04cb21cd6c?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">UK Visa Assistance</h1>
        <p>100% Success Rate. We guide you through the Tier 4 Student Visa process.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">The Student Visa Process Simplified</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Applying for a UK visa requires precision. A single missing document can result in a refusal. We provide a meticulous review of your documents before submission.
        </p>

        <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #E65100;">Required Documents Checklist</h3>
            <ul style="color: #555; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li><strong>CAS Letter:</strong> Confirmation of Acceptance for Studies from your University.</li>
                <li><strong>Financial Evidence:</strong> Bank statements showing sufficient funds for tuition and 9 months of living expenses (held for 28 consecutive days).</li>
                <li><strong>TB Test Certificate:</strong> Required for students from specific countries (including Pakistan).</li>
                <li><strong>Academic Qualifications:</strong> Your original transcripts and degree certificates.</li>
                <li><strong>ATAS Certificate:</strong> If applicable to your specific course type.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; background: #FFF3E0; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid #FF9800;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #E65100;">Don't Risk a Visa Rejection</h2>
            <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 25px;">Our certified Visa Specialists will conduct mock interviews and prepare your file flawlessly.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="calc-btn-primary" style="background: #E65100; display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 15px 40px;">Sign in & Book Visa Advisor</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>